project_descr: The project aims to facilitate the continuing development and expansion of the Association of Professional Journalists in Kosovo as a vital mechanism for oversight and accountability in Kosovo

outputs.output_descr: The project aims at reaching three key results (1) improve the capacities of the Association of Professional Journalists in Kosovo (AGPK), (2) establish and/or revise freedom of expression regulatory  framework and implementation, (3) access to information and quality of reporting for the disadvantaged  groups improved.

project_title: association of the professional journalists of kosovo
